<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>과학 한 모금 — 매일의 과학을 한 모금씩</title>
<meta name="description" content="{{ siteDescription }}">
<link rel="icon" href="/assets/favicon.svg">
{% set ogType = "website" %}
{% include "seo.njk" %}
{% include "_style.njk" %}
</head>
<body>
<header class="site-head hero">
  <span class="brand-big">☕ 과학 한 모금</span>
  <p class="tagline">매일의 과학을 한 모금씩</p>
</header>
{% include "_nav.njk" %}

{%- set posts = collections.post | reverse %}
{%- set featured = posts[0] %}
<main class="toc-wrap">
  {%- if featured %}
  <a class="feature-card" href="{{ featured.url }}">
    <span class="cat">{{ featured.data.category }}</span>
    <h2>{{ featured.data.title }}</h2>
    <p class="fc-deck">{{ featured.data.deck }}</p>
    <span class="fc-meta">{{ featured.data.displayDate }} · 가장 최근 기사</span>
  </a>
  {%- endif %}

  {%- set beyond = collections.deepdive | reverse | first %}
  <section class="other-boards">
    {%- if beyond %}
    <a class="board-card" href="{{ beyond.url }}">
      <span class="board-label">📝 기사 그 너머</span>
      <h3>{{ beyond.data.title }}</h3>
      <p>{{ beyond.data.deck }}</p>
    </a>
    {%- endif %}
    <a class="board-card board-soon" href="/memo/">
      <span class="board-label">✍️ 과저씨의 메모장</span>
      <h3>곧 찾아옵니다</h3>
      <p>AI·과학 뒷이야기·소식</p>
    </a>
    <a class="board-card board-soon" href="/world/">
      <span class="board-label">🌍 실험실과 차트</span>
      <h3>곧 찾아옵니다</h3>
      <p>과학과 경제가 만나는 자리</p>
    </a>
  </section>

  {%- if posts.length > 1 %}
  <div class="post-list">
    {%- for post in posts %}
    {%- if not loop.first %}
    <a class="post-row" href="{{ post.url }}">
      <div class="pr-head">
        <span class="cat cat-sm">{{ post.data.category }}</span>
        <time>{{ post.data.displayDate }}</time>
      </div>
      <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
      <p>{{ post.data.deck }}</p>
    </a>
    {%- endif %}
    {%- endfor %}
  </div>
  {%- endif %}
</main>

<footer class="site-foot">
  <a class="feedback-link" href="mailto:ohyuk1220@naver.com?subject=과학 한 모금 의견·불편한 점">💬 불편한 점·의견 보내기</a>
  <span>{{ collections.post | length }}편의 기사 · 전시실 뒷방</span>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
